              <div style="height:6px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:8px">
                <div style="height:100%;width:100%;background:var(--tw-teal);border-radius:999px"></div>
              </div>
              <div style="font-family:var(--tw-font-body);font-size:12.5px;color:var(--tw-teal-700);line-height:1.45;opacity:0.85">Cushion for inflation and surprise repairs. Resale values reflect it; lenders quote it back.</div>
